 <li>Have made a significant impact in their profession and/or community by developing or implementing an innovative program, process or product within the Black community.</li> 
 <li>Have reflected and recognized, in their actions and deeds, the importance of their Ryerson education and through their stature, integrity and ability they inspire students, faculty and staff within the Black community, both on and off-campus.</li> 
</ul> 
